text: Cameron Pimentel (born 13 April 1991) is a Bermudian competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Bermuda Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Sailors at the 2015 Pan American Games
